==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Whoremaster
<hw>Whore"mas`ter</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A
man who practices lewdness; a lecher; a whoremonger.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>One keeps or procures whores for others; a pimp; a
procurer.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Whoremasterly</ent>⟦br⟧
